      <p style="font-size:13px; color:var(--ink-dim); max-width:46rem; margin-bottom:10px;">
        Add your physical address, phone number, and hours here. We can also embed a Google Map and a simple contact form in the next iteration.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size:13px; color:var(--ink-dim);">
        Example: 123 Main Street, Your City, ST 29926 Â· (555) 555-5555
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <footer class="site-footer">
